summary: Maisie Williams Wraps Filming ‘Game of Thrones’ Season 8
title: Maisie Williams Wraps Filming ‘Game of Thrones’ Season 8
excerpt: Winter is coming… or leaving? As Maisie Williams, our beloved Arya Stark has finished filming her part in the upcoming final season of the praised HBO show Game of Thrones, announcing it with…
description: Although the final season is only six episodes long, the schedule for its filming has been extensive, as the producers are aiming for the most epic season as of yet. The series has not finished filming, but probably her hashtag hints that she’s the last female crew member to have shot her part, as Williams is extremely careful of spoilers in any post she makes.
